{
  "stem": "27507.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But it was, of course, something fantastic to have your own flat in the-- your own furniture and your own flat in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we still continued--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well it was lucky because, because, because people were living already-- at this stage in the ghetto, the majority of the population were-- if they were lucky, they had one room--",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, for the whole family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if they were unlucky-- of course, it helped that we were from Warsaw and that we still had some money.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People who were coming without anything from outside Warsaw, particularly those that were coming from little towns around, they had nothing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were coming, and they were put in a kind of a mass houses, which were-- there were some of them which were called points, [NON-ENGLISH] And they had to live there maybe whole family to a room or maybe even more than one whole family to a room.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had-- and there was-- and they had, of course, probably no food and then the food supply was-- the official food supply was never enough to keep one alive.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they had-- and there was no heating and people were spending-- in those places if they were able to warm themselves, it was only by a staying in bed.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So some of them were staying all day in bed covering all possible covers and so on just to keep warm.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And but not everybody could stay in bed because they had as well to go and look for some way of, of, of keeping their body together.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they had to look for to try to, to, to, trade or to buy and sell something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in winter, it's very hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
